T02TD1958E:85b-1: krishna ya m'a ri ya bhi sa ma ya kra ma /
T02TD1958E:85b-3: gshin rje gshed nag po'i mngon par rtogs pa'i rim pa /
T02TD1958E:85b-4: bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1958E:85b-5: gus pas bla ma dang ni gshin rje gshed nag rdo rje ni //
T02TD1958E:85b-6: nyid mtshungs dang 'dus bde bas yongs gang gzhan gyi don 'jug pa //
T02TD1958E:85b-7: rdo rje ral gri 'khor lo chu skyes gri gug thod pa phyag na bsnams //
T02TD1958E:85b-8: zhal gsum pa la 'jigs pa sel mdzad de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1958E:85b-9: dus dgra nag po sgrub pa nyid //
T02TD1958E:85b-10: gang zhig 'dod nas de nyid rig / dbang bskur la sogs thob pa dag / de yi bsgom pa'i rim pa 'di //
T02TD1958E:85b-11: byis pas bde bar rtogs phyir dang //
T02TD1958E:85b-12: mtshungs pa rnams kyis dran phyir dang //
T02TD1958E:85b-13: gong ma byis pa'i tshig dag la //
T02TD1958E:85b-14: mgu ba bskyed phyir bri bar bya //
T02TD1958E:85b-15: sbyin dang tshul khrims la sogs ldan //
T02TD1958E:85b-16: sems can don dga' blo dang ldan //
T02TD1958E:85b-17: byams la sogs yon tan rdzogs//
T02TD1958E:85b-18: dad dang thos pas rnam brgyan pas //
T02TD1958E:85b-19: dang por gdong la sogs bkru ba //
T02TD1958E:85b-20: snying rje'i bdag nyid sngon du bya //
T02TD1958E:85b-21: dben pa'i gnas su brtsam bya ste /
T02TD1958E:85b-22: dur khrod la sogs bde gnas la //
T02TD1958E:85b-24: shin tu 'od gsal zla ba blta //
T02TD1958E:85b-25: ya yig sngon po 'od mdzes pa //
T02TD1958E:85b-26: sems can 'byor pa'i don byed blta //
T02TD1958E:85b-27: nam mkha'i khams ni kun gang ba'i //
T02TD1958E:85b-28: bla ma dang ni rdzogs sangs bsgom //
T02TD1958E:85b-29: lus kyi bkod pa byas nas ni //
T02TD1958E:85b-30: de rnams dmigs nas phyag kyang bya //
T02TD1958E:85b-31: ts'artsi k'a sogs kyis mchod pa //
T02TD1958E:85b-32: byas la sdig pa bshags pa'ang bya //
T02TD1958E:85b-33: lus dang ngag dang yid kyis sdig bgyis dang bgyid du stsal ba dang //
T02TD1958E:85b-34: gang yang rjes su yi rang ba //
T02TD1958E:85b-35: de ni mgon la dus gsum bshags //
T02TD1958E:85b-36: rdzogs sangs rgyas dang de yi sras //
T02TD1958E:85b-37: 'phags pa rnams kyis bsags pa yi //
T02TD1958E:85b-38: bsod nams kun la rjes yi rang //
T02TD1958E:85b-39: dam pa'i chos dang tshogs mchog bcas //
T02TD1958E:85b-40: rdzogs sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi //
T02TD1958E:85b-41: yon tan rgya mtsho khyed rnams la //
T02TD1958E:85b-42: bdag gis lus ni dbul bar bgyi //
T02TD1958E:85b-43: dam pa'i chos kun ston mdzad pa'i //
T02TD1958E:85b-44: sgra yis mdzes pas khyed bzhugs gsol //
T02TD1958E:85b-45: yang dag rdzogs sangs sras bcas pa'i //
T02TD1958E:85b-46: sbyin pa la sogs ngo bo la //
T02TD1958E:86a-2: rab tu dga' bas gnas par bgyi //
T02TD1958E:86a-3: sems can don phyir yang dag rdzogs //
T02TD1958E:86a-4: byang chub sems ni bskyed par bgyi //
T02TD1958E:86a-5: dge ba yang dag gang bsags pa //
T02TD1958E:86a-6: byang chub tu ni bsngo bar bgyi //
T02TD1958E:86a-7: dpal ldan gshin rje gshed gyur nas //
T02TD1958E:86a-8: bdag gis 'gro la phan bgyi'o zhes //
T02TD1958E:86a-9: smon lam de ltar btab nas ni //
T02TD1958E:86a-10: de nas blo yis gshegs su gsol //
T02TD1958E:86a-11: snying rjes cho ga bzhin bltas nas //
T02TD1958E:86a-12: sna tshogs stong par rnam par bsam //
T02TD1958E:86a-13: ngo bo nyid dang bral ba'i phyir //
T02TD1958E:86a-14: rgyu nyid kyi ni mtshan ma med //
T02TD1958E:86a-15: rnam par rtog pa spangs pa'i phyir //
T02TD1958E:86a-16: smon pa nyid kyang rnam par spangs //
T02TD1958E:86a-17: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1958E:86a-18: sems can de brtan par byas nas ni //
T02TD1958E:86a-19: ram las byung ba'i nyi ma la //
T02TD1958E:86a-20: h'um las byung ba'i mdog sngon po //
T02TD1958E:86a-22: rdo rje kun nas rtse lnga pa //
T02TD1958E:86a-23: bsrung ba'i don du bsgom par bya //
T02TD1958E:86a-25: rab gur yang de bzhin no //
T02TD1958E:86a-26: sangs rgyas zhing ni rnam sbyang phyir //
T02TD1958E:86a-27: yang dag bsgom pa yang brtsam bya //
T02TD1958E:86a-28: de la sna tshogs pad zla bar //
T02TD1958E:86a-29: rdo rje bzang po'i lus byung ba'i //
T02TD1958E:86a-30: chos 'byung dkar po gru gsum pa'o //
T02TD1958E:86a-31: nang du sna tshogs pad rdo rje //
T02TD1958E:86a-32: gyen 'greng mkha' mnyam bsgom par bya //
T02TD1958E:86a-33: de nang du ni dkyil 'khor yang //
T02TD1958E:86a-34: bhr'um yig 'khor lo las byung ba'i //
T02TD1958E:86a-35: rtag pa'i yan lag las byung ba //
T02TD1958E:86a-36: gru bzhi pa la sgo bzhi pa //
T02TD1958E:86a-37: rta babs bzhi yis mdzes par brgyan //
T02TD1958E:86a-38: do shal se mo do yis mdzes //
T02TD1958E:86a-39: ba dan rtse mo sna tshogs la //
T02TD1958E:86a-40: rlung gis bskyod pa'i dril bur ldan //
T02TD1958E:86a-41: sna tshogs rdo rje rnam par mnan //
T02TD1958E:86a-42: zla ba nyi ma rgyal ba'i gdan //
T02TD1958E:86a-43: shar gyi phyogs ni dkar po che //
T02TD1958E:86a-44: lho phyogs ser po yang dag ldan //
T02TD1958E:86a-45: nub kyi cha ni dmar pe ste //
T02TD1958E:86a-46: byang phyogs ma rgad lta bu'o //
T02TD1958E:86a-47: dbang ldan sngon po'i mdog 'dra ba //
T02TD1958E:86a-48: dbus kyi cha ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD1958E:86a-49: 'di bzhin sna tshogs rdo rje dang //
T02TD1958E:86a-50: rtsig ngos steng g-yogs kyang bsgom bya //
T02TD1958E:86a-51: rnam pa lnga ni rnam bsgom la //
T02TD1958E:86a-52: sangs rgyas gzugs ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD1958E:86a-53: dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang nyid de //
T02TD1958E:86a-54: rnam pa lnga yin gshin rje rnams //
T02TD1958E:86a-55: 'jigs byed sangs rgyas gzugs zhes grags //
T02TD1958E:86a-56: de yi dbye ba bshad par bya //
T02TD1958E:86b-0: sna tshogs gdan @86b gyi lte ba la //
T02TD1958E:86b-1: padma zla ba dbyangs yi gzung //
T02TD1958E:86b-2: de nas zla ba ka sogs pa //
T02TD1958E:86b-3: da dha da dha ya la yang //
T02TD1958E:86b-4: bsnan pa gnyis 'gyur las byung ba /
T02TD1958E:86b-5: zla ba dmar po bsgom par bya //
T02TD1958E:86b-6: 'di dag yongs su rdzogs pa ni //
T02TD1958E:86b-7: me long lta bu'i ye shes brjod //
T02TD1958E:86b-8: de dag gcig gyur mnyam pa nyid //
T02TD1958E:86b-9: der skyes h'um ni so sor rtog / bya ba nan tan ldan ye shes //
T02TD1958E:86b-10: de las skyes pa'i rdo rje'o //
T02TD1958E:86b-11: nyi ma'i mdangs ldan nor bu 'dra //
T02TD1958E:86b-12: sa bon dang bcas 'od zer 'khrug / aom badzra a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1958E:86b-13: zhes bya bas nga rgyal bya'o //
T02TD1958E:86b-14: de las skya rengs dang po'i mdog can thub pa'i tshogs kyis mdzes pa nyid mtshungs kyis 'khyud sku //
T02TD1958E:86b-15: sgeg dang khro bo'i gzugs can bde mchog gi rang bzhin dkar dang sngo dang dmar ba'i zhal //
T02TD1958E:86b-16: g-yon brkyang ba yis gnas pa 'bar ba'i ral gri rdo rje gri gug sor mdzad cing //
T02TD1958E:86b-17: 'khor lo chu skyes snod ni 'od zer 'phro ba g-yas dang g-yon pa'i phyag na bsnams //
T02TD1958E:86b-18: chos dbyings ye shes ngo bo ni //
T02TD1958E:86b-19: rdo rje 'chang gi bdag nyid gang //
T02TD1958E:86b-20: rnam pa lnga yi ngo bo nyid //
T02TD1958E:86b-21: rnal 'byor zhes ni brjod pa yin //
T02TD1958E:86b-24: 'gro ba gsum la gzigs nas kyang //
T02TD1958E:86b-26: sna tshogs sangs rgyas gzugs su bya //
T02TD1958E:86b-27: dga' bde dam pa'i gzugs kyis ni //
T02TD1958E:86b-28: rang gi lus la mnyam pra gzhug / kun rtog thams cad spangs pa yi //
T02TD1958E:86b-29: longs spyod rdzogs par bdag nyid bsgom //
T02TD1958E:86b-30: de ltar sngags mchog yi ge gsum //
T02TD1958E:86b-31: dmar po ho: gnyis kyi brten pa //
T02TD1958E:86b-32: ji ltar skar mda' 'pho ba bzhin //
T02TD1958E:86b-33: byang chub sems ni de nas gzhug /
T02TD1958E:86b-34: snying rje chags pa'i sems nyid kyis //
T02TD1958E:86b-35: rdo rje 'chang nyid rang yang zhu //
T02TD1958E:86b-36: ts'artsi k'a sogs byams sogs pas //
T02TD1958E:86b-37: 'khor lo'i gtso bo skul bar byed //
T02TD1958E:86b-38: snying rjes khros pa'i sgrol bzhengs //
T02TD1958E:86b-39: khams gsum kun gyi gti mug sol //
T02TD1958E:86b-40: dad sgrol rtsol med ma bzhugs bzhengs //
T02TD1958E:86b-41: bdud 'di dag las rgyal bar mdzod //
T02TD1958E:86b-42: 'jig rten mgon pos stong nyid ci ste bzhugs //
T02TD1958E:86b-43: dad dgrol 'jig rten bsod nams kyis bzhengs shig / byang chub 'dod pa'i 'jig rten mgron bos nas //
T02TD1958E:86b-44: ji ltar stong pa nyid ni sems par byed //
T02TD1958E:86b-45: bskyal nas khu ba der thim par //
T02TD1958E:87a-2: de lta'i glu yi ngo nyid du //
T02TD1958E:87a-3: de la rgud pa ltar bsams nas //
T02TD1958E:87a-4: khu ba'i gzugs ni yongs gyur te //
T02TD1958E:87a-5: yam sngon nyi ma las byung ba //
T02TD1958E:87a-6: khro bo sngon po 'phro bar bcas //
T02TD1958E:87a-7: rus pa'i rgyan gyis rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1958E:87a-8: rva rnon 'bar zhing spu ser skya //
T02TD1958E:87a-9: rmig pas brko zhing 'jigs sbyin pa'i //
T02TD1958E:87a-10: ma he yi ni rgyab gnas pa'i //
T02TD1958E:87a-11: rdo rje sngon po 'od dang bcas //
T02TD1958E:87a-12: sa bon bcas pa de'i 'od kyis //
T02TD1958E:87a-14: bdag nyid la ni yang dag zhugs //
T02TD1958E:87a-16: ma he'i rdo rje rnam bsgoms nas //
T02TD1958E:87a-17: dkyil 'khor gtso bo bsgom par bya //
T02TD1958E:87a-19: 'od zer drag po spros pas skrod //
T02TD1958E:87a-20: drag po mun 'dra gzugs drag po //
T02TD1958E:87a-22: sma ra smin ma mgo skyes ser //
T02TD1958E:87a-23: g-yon brkyang pa yi gnas pa yis //
T02TD1958E:87a-24: gshin rje dran pa med par byed //
T02TD1958E:87a-25: rtsa ba'i zhal ni nag po ste //
T02TD1958E:87a-27: g-yon pa khrag dang 'dra bar bshad //
T02TD1958E:87a-28: rdo rje rgyan gyis rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1958E:87a-29: thung zhing gsus pa 'phyang la sbom //
T02TD1958E:87a-30: mgo bo'i phreng bas rnam par 'phyang //
T02TD1958E:87a-31: g-yas dang g-yon gyi phyag dag la //
T02TD1958E:87a-32: thod pa dang ni gri gug bsnams //
T02TD1958E:87a-33: nyid mtshungs shes rab kyis 'khyud cing//
T02TD1958E:87a-35: g-yas pa'i phyag ni lhag ma la //
T02TD1958E:87a-36: rdo rje gral gri 'bar ba bsnams //
T02TD1958E:87a-37: 'khor lo chu skyes g-yon dag la //
T02TD1958E:87a-38: sprul gyi dbang pos rgyan du byas //
T02TD1958E:87a-39: sprul rgyan sngon po dga' bo yis //
T02TD1958E:87a-40: skra bcings shin tu 'jigs par byed //
T02TD1958E:87a-41: taksha ka klu dmar po yis rna cha gdub kor byas pas 'jigs //
T02TD1958E:87a-42: rigs ldan khro bo dpung rgyan te //
T02TD1958E:87a-43: dung skyong zhes bya'i klu de ni //
T02TD1958E:87a-44: ser po lag pa'i gdu bu byas //
T02TD1958E:87a-45: padma dkar pos do shal byas /
T02TD1958E:87a-46: karko ta ni ljang gu ste //
T02TD1958E:87a-47: ser ral kha ru byas pas mdzes //
T02TD1958E:87a-48: bdud rtsi'i mdog dang 'dra ba yi //
T02TD1958E:87a-49: nor rgyas bus ni ska rags byas //
T02TD1958E:87a-50: padma'i rtsa ba ltar dkar mdog / padma chen po rkang gdub yin //
T02TD1958E:87a-51: kun kyang phut sgra drag po sgrogs //
T02TD1958E:87a-52: lce gnyis mche ba'i phreng ba can //
T02TD1958E:87a-54: gshin rje 'dul ba'i gzugs su shes //
T02TD1958E:87a-55: rnam par rtog pa spang ba'i phyir //
T02TD1958E:87a-56: sngags kyis yang dag byin gyis brlabs //
T02TD1958E:87b-0: @87b aom dharma dh'a tu sva bh'a ba a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1958E:87b-1: zhes bya ba ni rjes su rnal 'byor ro //
T02TD1958E:87b-2: rang snying sa bon 'od kyis bkug / yang dag rdzogs sangs mkha' khyab pa //
T02TD1958E:87b-3: kun du kha nas gzhug par bya //
T02TD1958E:87b-4: bde ba myong bas snying gar bzhu //
T02TD1958E:87b-5: byas nas blo ldan khu ba de //
T02TD1958E:87b-6: rdo rje'i lam nas spro bar bya //
T02TD1958E:87b-7: nyid mtshungs padma'i nang du gnas //
T02TD1958E:87b-8: sa bon ngo bo ldan byas te //
T02TD1958E:87b-9: sa bon las byung 'khor lo mchog / sa bon kun gyi byin rlabs la //
T02TD1958E:87b-10: me stag tshogs kyis gsal gyur pa //
T02TD1958E:87b-11: blo ldan cho ga bzhin du bsgom //
T02TD1958E:87b-12: dkyil du yam sngon las byung ba //
T02TD1958E:87b-13: bstan pa'i mtshan ldan 'khor lo can //
T02TD1958E:87b-14: shar du kshe dang 'khor los byung //
T02TD1958E:87b-15: rtag pa phrag drug dkar po'o //
T02TD1958E:87b-16: gnas na 'khor lo ral gri phyag //
T02TD1958E:87b-17: g-yon na rin chen chu skyes 'dzin //
T02TD1958E:87b-18: lha ru ma dang rin chen las //
T02TD1958E:87b-19: byung ba rin chen 'byung ldan te //
T02TD1958E:87b-20: btso ma gser gyi mdog 'dra ba //
T02TD1958E:87b-21: g-yas na rin chen ral gri bsnams //
T02TD1958E:87b-22: phyag g-yon 'khor lo chu skyes so //
T02TD1958E:87b-23: nub tu 'dod chags rdo rje can //
T02TD1958E:87b-24: me dang padma las byung ba //
T02TD1958E:87b-25: padma r'a ga 'dra ba'i mdog / padma ral gri rin chen dang //
T02TD1958E:87b-26: 'khor lo g-yas g-yon phyag na dgod //
T02TD1958E:87b-27: da dang ral gri las byung ba //
T02TD1958E:87b-28: ljang gu phrag dog gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1958E:87b-29: g-yas na ral gri 'khor lo bsnams //
T02TD1958E:87b-30: mdzes pa nor bu padma g-yon //
T02TD1958E:87b-31: khro bo'i gzugs can thams cad kyang //
T02TD1958E:87b-32: zhe sdang gshin rje mtshan nyid 'dra //
T02TD1958E:87b-33: de dag rtsa ba'i phyag gnyis pa //
T02TD1958E:87b-34: gri gug dang ni thod pa bsam //
T02TD1958E:87b-35: rang gi shes rab lus dag dang //
T02TD1958E:87b-36: bde ba'i ngo bor gnyis med gyur //
T02TD1958E:87b-37: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor mnyam par gnon //
T02TD1958E:87b-38: rtag pa zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la //
T02TD1958E:87b-39: rdo rje rtsibs kyi rtsar gnas pa //
T02TD1958E:87b-40: sems can don mdzad bsgom par bya //
T02TD1958E:87b-41: shar sgor ya dang tho ba las //
T02TD1958E:87b-42: byung ba sngon po'i gzugs can te /
T02TD1958E:87b-43: g-yas na tho ba ral gri 'dzin //
T02TD1958E:87b-44: nor bu mchog dang padma g-yon //
T02TD1958E:87b-45: tho ba zhe sdang gshin gshed 'dra //
T02TD1958E:87b-46: rtsi dang dbyug pa las byung lhor //
T02TD1958E:87b-47: dbyug pa gshin gshed mdog dkar po'o //
T02TD1958E:87b-48: dbyug par ral gri pad 'khor lo //
T02TD1958E:87b-49: nub tu padma gshin rje gshed /
T02TD1958E:87b-51: byang du ral gri gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1958E:87b-52: ra las phrag dog mthar byed mtshungs //
T02TD1958E:87b-53: chu skyes sngon po'i khyad par gyis //
T02TD1958E:87b-54: bsgyur ba lta chung la 'jigs byin //
T02TD1958E:88a-0: @88a * // kun kyang sbrul gyis rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1958E:88a-3: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa //
T02TD1958E:88a-4: mche ba gtsigs shing 'jigs pa'i zhal //
T02TD1958E:88a-5: gri gug thod pa 'dzin par mdzad //
T02TD1958E:88a-6: sna tshogs rdo rje'i mtshams bzhi ru //
T02TD1958E:88a-7: de bzhin lha mo zla bar gnas //
T02TD1958E:88a-8: shar lhor dza dang 'khor lo las //
T02TD1958E:88a-9: lha mo rdo rje ts'a rtsi k'a //
T02TD1958E:88a-10: skem mo dkar mo cher khro ba //
T02TD1958E:88a-11: gti mug gshin rje gshed dang mtshungs //
T02TD1958E:88a-12: lho nub mtshams su sa dang ni //
T02TD1958E:88a-13: rdo rje las byung rdo rje phag / khro zhing phag gi gdong pa can //
T02TD1958E:88a-14: zhe sdang gshin rje gshed dang mtshungs //
T02TD1958E:88a-15: nub dang byang gi mtshams su ni //
T02TD1958E:88a-16: rab tu zhi ba'i dbyang can ma //
T02TD1958E:88a-17: do las byung ba rab tu dmar //
T02TD1958E:88a-18: 'dod chags gshin rje gshed dang mtshungs //
T02TD1958E:88a-19: byang shar mtshams su ru las ni //
T02TD1958E:88a-20: goo r'i ljang gu 'jigs byed ma //
T02TD1958E:88a-21: phrag dog gshin rje gshed dang mtshungs //
T02TD1958E:88a-22: sngon po'i g-yas pa dkar po ste //
T02TD1958E:88a-23: dkar po'i g-yas pa sngon po yin //
T02TD1958E:88a-24: de dag zhal g-yon dmar po'o //
T02TD1958E:88a-25: gzhan gyi sngo dang dkar ba'o //
T02TD1958E:88a-26: mtshams bzhin na yo ni r'a las //
T02TD1958E:88a-28: ji ltar rang rang sngags bstan pa //
T02TD1958E:88a-29: bskyed la blo ldan gyis spro bya //
T02TD1958E:88a-30: h'ri: shtri: la sogs sngags sgra yis //
T02TD1958E:88a-31: dkyil 'khor bdag po bskul bar bya / sprul pa dpag med spros byas la //
T02TD1958E:88a-32: sems can don ni mchog byas nas //
T02TD1958E:88a-33: rnam pa kun gyis rang lus la //
T02TD1958E:88a-34: khro bo dpa' bo gzhug par bya //
T02TD1958E:88a-35: shar du dzi ni dzik ces pas //
T02TD1958E:88a-36: rmongs pas rmongs pa mthar byed pa //
T02TD1958E:88a-37: rtsibs rtsa'i sna tshogs padma dang //
T02TD1958E:88a-38: zla ba la ni de bzhin bzhag / ratna dhrik ces bya ba yis //
T02TD1958E:88a-39: lho rtsibs rtsa bar pad nyi la //
T02TD1958E:88a-40: phra ma zhes bya ba bkug nas ni //
T02TD1958E:88a-41: cho ga bzhin du gzhag par bya //
T02TD1958E:88a-42: a'a ro lik ces sngags kyis //
T02TD1958E:88a-43: 'dod chags gshin rje gshed 'jigs byed la //
T02TD1958E:88a-44: nub tu padma nyi ma la /
T02TD1958E:88a-45: cho ga yis ni rnam par bsam //
T02TD1958E:88a-46: de nyid pradzny'a dhrik ces pas //
T02TD1958E:88a-47: phrag dog nag po 'jigs byed pa //
T02TD1958E:88a-49: cho ga bzhin du gzhag par bya //
T02TD1958E:88a-50: mudga ra dhrik de nyid kyis //
T02TD1958E:88a-51: shar sgo padma nyi ma la //
T02TD1958E:88a-52: tho ba mthar byed 'jigs byed pa //
T02TD1958E:88a-53: mkhas pas cho ga bzhin du bsam //
T02TD1958E:88b-0: danda dhrik @88b kyi sngags kyis ni //
T02TD1958E:88b-1: lho yi phyogs sgor gnas pa yi //
T02TD1958E:88b-2: dbyug pa gdul dka' gshin rje'i dgra //
T02TD1958E:88b-3: sna tshogs padma nyi mar dgod //
T02TD1958E:88b-5: padma gshin rje gcod byed pa //
T02TD1958E:88b-6: nub sgor padma nyi ma la //
T02TD1958E:88b-7: stobs chen khro bo bsgom par bya //
T02TD1958E:88b-8: khadga dhrik gi de nyid kyis //
T02TD1958E:88b-9: ral gri gshin rje zad byed pa //
T02TD1958E:88b-10: byang du padma nyi ma la //
T02TD1958E:88b-11: bdud tshar gcod pa bsam par bya //
T02TD1958E:88b-12: sna tshogs rdo rje'i mtshams bzhi ru //
T02TD1958E:88b-13: 'di ltar lha mo mchog bzhi bsgom //
T02TD1958E:88b-14: shar lho mtshams kyi lha mo ni //
T02TD1958E:88b-15: skem mo khro la 'od bzang ma //
T02TD1958E:88b-16: mo ha ra ti'i sngags kyis ni //
T02TD1958E:88b-17: sna tshogs padma zla bar gnas //
T02TD1958E:88b-18: de yi nub tu rigs mchog ma //
T02TD1958E:88b-19: rdo rje phag mo zhes bya ba //
T02TD1958E:88b-20: dve sha ra ti'i sngags kyis ni //
T02TD1958E:88b-21: padma zla bar mkhas pas dgod //
T02TD1958E:88b-22: de yi byang gi mtshams su ni //
T02TD1958E:88b-23: r'a ga ra ti'i gsang sngags kyis //
T02TD1958E:88b-24: padma zla bar dbyangs can dgod //
T02TD1958E:88b-25: de yi shar du goo r'i ma //
T02TD1958E:88b-26: padma zla bar badzra ra ti yis //
T02TD1958E:88b-28: dkyil 'khor phyi yi mtshams bzhi ru //
T02TD1958E:88b-29: de nyid gsum gyi thod pa ste //
T02TD1958E:88b-30: de ltar dkyil 'khor dam pa spro //
T02TD1958E:88b-31: bde ba dang bcas bstan par bya //
T02TD1958E:88b-32: 'khor lo snga ma der thim par //
T02TD1958E:88b-33: mnyam par bzhag pas blta bar bya //
T02TD1958E:88b-35: nag po gshin rje 'jigs byed kyi //
T02TD1958E:88b-36: dkyil 'khor ba yi ngo bo nyid //
T02TD1958E:88b-37: lus dang mig sogs lha rnams kyis //
T02TD1958E:88b-38: mngon par byin gyis brlab par bya //
T02TD1958E:88b-39: 'khor lo kshim las gti mug mtshungs //
T02TD1958E:88b-40: cung zhig khro ba mig la ste //
T02TD1958E:88b-41: rdo rje mig ni mkhas pas bsgom //
T02TD1958E:88b-42: rna bar dzram las rdo rje las //
T02TD1958E:88b-43: nag po rdo rje dang mtshungs pa //
T02TD1958E:88b-44: sna la kham dang rin chen las //
T02TD1958E:88b-45: phra ma dang mtshungs zla ba la //
T02TD1958E:88b-46: lce la gam dang padma las //
T02TD1958E:88b-47: padma ri bong can la bsam //
T02TD1958E:88b-48: 'dod chags dang mtshungs kam ral gri //
T02TD1958E:88b-49: padma ri bong can bzhugs sku //
T02TD1958E:88b-50: rdo rje phrag dog gshin gshed mtshungs //
T02TD1958E:88b-51: lus zhes bya ba dpral ba la'o //
T02TD1958E:88b-52: sam dang rdo rjes lte ba'i steng //
T02TD1958E:88b-54: sgeg dang khro ba'i gzugs can no //
T02TD1958E:88b-55: yan lag drug la dgod pa 'di //
T02TD1958E:88b-56: mngon shes don ni sgrub phyir bshad //
T02TD1958E:88b-57: snying gar h'um dang rdo rje las //
T02TD1958E:88b-58: gshin rje 'joms pa'i thugs rdo rje //
T02TD1958E:88b-59: mdog dang mtshon char yang dag ldan //
T02TD1958E:89a-3: ngag gi rdo rje bsam par bya //
T02TD1958E:89a-4: mgo bor aom dang 'khor lo las //
T02TD1958E:89a-6: phyag dang sku mdog mtshon chas ldan //
T02TD1958E:89a-7: rdo rje sku mchog de nyid gsum //
T02TD1958E:89a-8: bskyed la nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor gnas pa'i //
T02TD1958E:89a-9: sangs rgyas mchog la sngags kyis ni //
T02TD1958E:89a-10: byin gyis brlab pa dag kyang bya //
T02TD1958E:89a-11: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta tsitta badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1958E:89a-12: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta w'a ka badzra sva bh'a a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1958E:89a-13: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta w'a ka badzra sva bh'a a'atma ko& ham //
T02TD1958E:89a-14: rang snying sa bon 'od zer gyis //
T02TD1958E:89a-15: phyogs bzhugs sangs rgyas sra dang bcas //
T02TD1958E:89a-16: bkug nas mdun du blta bar bya //
T02TD1958E:89a-17: de dag las ni spros pa yi //
T02TD1958E:89a-18: zla 'dra ts'a rtsi k'a sogs kyis //
T02TD1958E:89a-19: bzung ba'i bum pa dag gis ni //
T02TD1958E:89a-20: de dag bkra shis glu la sogs //
T02TD1958E:89a-21: dang dir dbyangs kyang yang byas la //
T02TD1958E:89a-22: bdag nyid dam ni gzhan dag kyang //
T02TD1958E:89a-23: dbang bskur ba ni bsam par bya /
T02TD1958E:89a-24: gshin rje gshed nag mgo la'o //
T02TD1958E:89a-25: bdag nyid mgo la rdo rje 'chang //
T02TD1958E:89a-26: rang snying sa bon 'od zer gyis //
T02TD1958E:89a-27: ye shes 'khor lo spyan drangs la //
T02TD1958E:89a-28: rang gi mdun du blta bar bya //
T02TD1958E:89a-29: khro bos bgegs rnams tshar bcad bsrung //
T02TD1958E:89a-30: yon chab zhabs bsil sogs phul la //
T02TD1958E:89a-31: aom mung+ga ra dza:'i sngags kyis dgug / aom danda h'um zhes bya bas gzhug / aom padma bam zhes bya bas bcing //
T02TD1958E:89a-32: aom khadga ho: zhes bya bas mnyes par bya'o //
T02TD1958E:89a-33: snying ga'i sa bon 'od kyis ni //
T02TD1958E:89a-34: sangs rgyas kun bkug zhal du gzhug //
T02TD1958E:89a-35: snying gar zhu bar byas par blta //
T02TD1958E:89a-36: rdo rje'i lam nas rjes byung nas //
T02TD1958E:89a-37: rang gi rig pa'i dbang dkyil du //
T02TD1958E:89a-38: zla ba las byung lha mo'i tshogs //
T02TD1958E:89a-39: me tog phreng ba sna tshogs sogs //
T02TD1958E:89a-40: lag pa'i snod du gzung byas pa //
T02TD1958E:89a-41: de dag sgeg dang bcas pas mchod //
T02TD1958E:89a-42: mchod pa'i glu ni yig 'phrog pa //
T02TD1958E:89a-43: bsgyur pa rnam pa sna tshogs pa //
T02TD1958E:89a-44: bde ba chen po gsal bar byed //
T02TD1958E:89a-45: aa kye kye gshin rje gshed nag po //
T02TD1958E:89a-46: srin po'i gzugs can rang bzhin khyod //
T02TD1958E:89a-47: bdag gis mthong na shin tu 'jigs //
T02TD1958E:89a-48: khros pa'i rang bzhin 'di thong mdzod //
T02TD1958E:89a-49: mi dang sa 'og rgya mtshor bcas //
T02TD1958E:89a-50: khyod kyi gar gyis g-yos par mdzod //
T02TD1958E:89b-0: khro bos ro langs @89b bzhin gar mdzod //
T02TD1958E:89b-1: rnam pa sna tshogs gzugs sprul cing //
T02TD1958E:89b-2: mdangs gnag tshad ni thung ba la //
T02TD1958E:89b-3: bde chen ngo bos gar mdzod ces //
T02TD1958E:89b-4: rdo rje dbyangs can ma gsol 'debs //
T02TD1958E:89b-5: hr'i: shti: sngags dang gar gyis khyod //
T02TD1958E:89b-6: drid pa gsum gyi 'khrul pa gcod //
T02TD1958E:89b-7: snying rje khros nas gar mdzad pa //
T02TD1958E:89b-8: 'gro bas mthong na ngo mtshar gyur //
T02TD1958E:89b-9: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta p'u dza badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1958E:89b-10: sgra yi tshigs rnams thams cad ni //
T02TD1958E:89b-11: brag ca 'dra bar blta byas nas //
T02TD1958E:89b-12: dkyil 'khor bas ni gtso bo bstod //
T02TD1958E:89b-13: res kyang de dag de bzhin no //
T02TD1958E:89b-14: gshin rje gshed po rab 'jigs pa //
T02TD1958E:89b-15: gti mug rdo rje'i ngo bo khyod //
T02TD1958E:89b-16: ston pa sangs rgyas kun rang bzhin //
T02TD1958E:89b-17: rdo rje sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1958E:89b-19: aom badzra k'i la ya badzra mung+ga ra a'a ko ta ya h'um phat ces brjod do //
T02TD1958E:89b-20: aom badzra auta k'i la ya zhes bya ba'i sngags dang phur bu phyung bar bsams pas //
T02TD1958E:89b-21: phyogs skyong ba thams cad gshin rje gshed du gyur par bsams te /
T02TD1958E:89b-22: de rnams la aom aindra ya hr'i: ya m'a yashti: ba ru n'a ya wi /
T02TD1958E:89b-28: tsandr'a ya h'um aark'a ya h'um /
T02TD1958E:89b-30: ba su dha ra ye phat /
T02TD1958E:89b-31: be ma tsi tr'a ya sv'a /
T02TD1958E:89b-33: h'a h'a h'a h'i h'i h'i h'um h'um h'um phem phem phem sv'a h'a /
T02TD1958E:89b-34: zhes bya ba'i sngags kyis gtor ma phul nas //
T02TD1958E:89b-35: khyed kyis bdag gi smon lam thams cad grub pa'i grogs mdzod cig ces brjod la //
T02TD1958E:89b-36: sarba de b'a di mu: zhes brjod pas //
T02TD1958E:89b-37: 'byung po thams cad slar btang bar bsam mo //
T02TD1958E:89b-38: de nas bdag gi dge ba 'dis bdag myur du 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed khro bo chen por gyur cig ces smon lam btab la /
T02TD1958E:89b-39: sngar bskyed pa'i gnas la sogs pa je chung 'dus nas bdag nyid kyi bar du mi snang bar bsam pa gshegs pa chen po zhes bya ste /
T02TD1958E:89b-40: aom manydzu shr'i sa ma ya //
T02TD1958E:89b-42: manydzru tve no pa tishtha dri dho me bha ba //
T02TD1958E:89b-43: su tu sh+yo me bha wa /
T02TD1958E:89b-44: aa nu rakto me bha wa /
T02TD1958E:89b-45: su po sh+yo me bha wa /
T02TD1958E:89b-46: sarba siddhi mme pra ya tstsha /
T02TD1958E:89b-47: sarba karma su tsa me tsittam shre ya: ku ru h'um /
T02TD1958E:89b-48: ha ha ha ha ho: bha ga w'a na /
T02TD1958E:89b-51: badz'i bha wa ma h'a sa ma ya sa tva a'a: zhes bya ba bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gyi yi ge brgya pa brjod par bya'o //
T02TD1958E:90a-2: bzlas pa'i bsnyen pa byas te /
T02TD1958E:90a-3: ji lta ba bzhin pa'i las kyi cho ga byas pa ni /
T02TD1958E:90a-4: zhi ba la sogs pa dngos grub bcu po gang yang rung ba ba 'grub par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1958E:90a-5: phal cher zla gsang nag rgyud la brten nas /
T02TD1958E:90a-6: khro bo chen 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed po yi //
T02TD1958E:90a-7: sgrub thabs ji bzhin gshed po yi //
T02TD1958E:90a-8: sgrub thabs ji bzhin byas pa'i dge ba 'dis /
T02TD1958E:90a-10: 'gro kun myur du gshin rje gshed gyur cig /'jam dpal gshin rje gshed khro bo chen po'i sgrub thabs slob dpon mkhas pa chen po dpal rdo rje'i blo mdzad pa rdzogs so//
